WEBVTT

00:03:27.758 --> 00:03:32.456
Even now, it's the way Ivan communicates

00:03:32.480 --> 00:03:33.842
what he wants,

00:03:34.311 --> 00:03:35.590
what he needs

00:03:36.392 --> 00:03:38.782
and also what he feels.

00:03:42.023 --> 00:03:45.222
But it wasn't just
Ivan's eye contact that mattered.

00:03:46.932 --> 00:03:48.896
Everyone else's did, too.

00:03:50.735 --> 00:03:54.725
How could I make people see
not only his autism,

00:03:54.749 --> 00:03:56.145
but see him the person

00:03:57.312 --> 00:03:58.981
and everything he can give;